00:08:47.980 --> 00:08:53.379
Hopefully we won't have to go through everything that Paul went through,

00:08:53.379 --> 00:08:57.379
but we know that we have difficult days ahead of us.

00:08:57.379 --> 00:09:01.379
But because we have a strong faith in Jesus' resurrection,

00:09:01.379 --> 00:09:05.379
we can go on walking in the truth.

00:09:05.379 --> 00:09:08.379
And like our brothers and sisters in the first century,

00:09:08.379 --> 00:09:13.379
